        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Improving Social Security's Service to Victims of Identity Theft Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Social Security Administration to provide a single point of contact for any individual whose Social Security account number has been misused. The single point of contact must track the individual's case to completion and coordinate with other specialized units to resolve case issues as quickly as possible.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
